      "comment" : "A period.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "· %@s/file" : {
      "comment" : "A label showing the time it takes to process a single file. The argument is the string “%.1f”.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "· checked %@" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "· checked %@"
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "· проверено %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "**Privacy-preserving analytics (open-source TelemetryDeck):** anonymous usage signals, never anything personal.\n**Off:** only five usage counts still send, so we can see Sentient is being used at all: how many people use it, Sidekick fires, proactive cards (made and fired), overnight runs, and home opens; counts only.\n**On:** those five, plus a fuller anonymous picture: onboarding progress, how long features run, and sync and health signals. Always just counts and categories, and nothing can be traced back to you." : {
      "comment" : "A list of privacy-preserving analytics that can be turned off.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Privacy-preserving analytics (open-source TelemetryDeck):** anonymous usage signals, never anything personal.\n**Off:** only five usage counts still send, so we can see Sentient is being used at all: how many people use it, Sidekick fires, proactive cards (made and fired), overnight runs, and home opens; counts only.\n**On:** those five, plus a fuller anonymous picture: onboarding progress, how long features run, and sync and health signals. Always just counts and categories, and nothing can be traced back to you."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Конфиденциальная аналитика (open-source TelemetryDeck):** анонимные сигналы использования, ничего личного.\n**Выкл.:** всё ещё уходят лишь пять счётчиков, чтобы понимать, что Sentient вообще используют: сколько людей, срабатывания Sidekick, проактивные карточки (созданные и запущенные), ночные прогоны и открытия дома; только числа.\n**Вкл.:** эти пять плюс более полная анонимная картина: прогресс онбординга, длительность функций, сигналы синхронизации и здоровья. Всегда только счётчики и категории — к вам это не привязать."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "**Privacy-preserving crash logs (open-source Sentry):** structure-only reports, like counts, error types, and stack traces, that help us fix your bugs. Switch them off and they stop completely." : {
      "comment" : "A privacy policy bullet point.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Privacy-preserving crash logs (open-source Sentry):** structure-only reports, like counts, error types, and stack traces, that help us fix your bugs. Switch them off and they stop completely."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Конфиденциальные логи сбоев (open-source Sentry):** только структура — счётчики, типы ошибок и стек-трейсы, чтобы чинить баги. Выключите — и они полностью остановятся."
          }
        }
      }
    },
