    "A tiny system helper that wakes your Mac at 3 AM so Sentient's on-device intelligence can work while you sleep.\n\nIt only runs while your Mac is plugged in and Sentient is open in your menu bar. Installed once with your password." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "A tiny system helper that wakes your Mac at 3 AM so Sentient's on-device intelligence can work while you sleep.\n\nIt only runs while your Mac is plugged in and Sentient is open in your menu bar. Installed once with your password."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Крошечный системный помощник будит Mac в 3:00, чтобы on-device интеллект Sentient работал, пока вы спите.\n\nОн запускается только когда Mac подключён к питанию и Sentient открыт в строке меню. Устанавливается один раз с паролем."
          }
        }
      }
    },
