    "Even the cloud backend is open source. Everything's verifiable." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Even the cloud backend is open source. Everything's verifiable."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Даже облачный бэкенд с открытым кодом. Всё проверяемо."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Even with this off, Sentient still sends a handful of extremely anonymized usage-count pings: how many people use Sentient, and how often core features fire (Sidekick, proactive cards, overnight runs, home opens). Counts only, through a privacy-first, open-source tool, so a two-person team can see our work is being used. Never your content, never anything personal." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Even with this off, Sentient still sends a handful of extremely anonymized usage-count pings: how many people use Sentient, and how often core features fire (Sidekick, proactive cards, overnight runs, home opens). Counts only, through a privacy-first, open-source tool, so a two-person team can see our work is being used. Never your content, never anything personal."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Даже когда это выключено, Sentient всё равно отправляет несколько крайне анонимизированных счётчиков: сколько людей пользуются Sentient и как часто срабатывают ключевые функции (Sidekick, proactive-карточки, ночные запуски, открытие домашнего экрана). Только счётчики через privacy-first open-source инструмент, чтобы команда из двух человек видела, что продукт используют. Никогда ваш контент, никогда ничего личного."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "EVENT LOG" : {
      "comment" : "The title of the log pane in the Hotkey Lab.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "Every morning, Sentient surfaces a few things worth doing, already done and waiting for your go. Tell it what you care about, and what to skip." : {
      "comment" : "Proactive intelligence instructions.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Every morning, Sentient surfaces a few things worth doing, already done and waiting for your go. Tell it what you care about, and what to skip."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Каждое утро Sentient показывает несколько дел, которые уже сделаны и ждут вашего «вперёд». Скажите, что важно, а что пропускать."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Every night at 3 AM, Sentient wakes your Mac to read what's new in your life, update your knowledge base, and prepare your morning suggestions. It only happens while your Mac is plugged in, and only if Sentient is still running in your menu bar. This quiet, on-device work is what keeps your Sentient alive and helpful." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Every night at 3 AM, Sentient wakes your Mac to read what's new in your life, update your knowledge base, and prepare your morning suggestions. It only happens while your Mac is plugged in, and only if Sentient is still running in your menu bar. This quiet, on-device work is what keeps your Sentient alive and helpful."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Каждую ночь в 3:00 Sentient будит ваш Mac, чтобы прочитать новое в вашей жизни, обновить базу знаний и подготовить утренние предложения. Это происходит только когда Mac подключён к питанию и Sentient всё ещё работает в строке меню. Эта тихая локальная работа и держит вашего Sentient живым и полезным."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Everything green means everything works." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Everything green means everything works."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Всё зелёное — значит всё работает."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Everything is still read locally; Full Disk Access is just how macOS lets Sentient open those databases. After granting, relaunch Sentient." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Everything is still read locally; Full Disk Access is just how macOS lets Sentient open those databases. After granting, relaunch Sentient."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Всё по-прежнему читается локально; полный доступ к диску — лишь способ macOS открыть эти базы. После выдачи перезапустите Sentient."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Everything Sentient made here has been removed. To finish, drag the Sentient OS app from your Applications folder to the Trash. Thank you for giving Sentient a try; it meant a lot to the two of us." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Everything Sentient made here has been removed. To finish, drag the Sentient OS app from your Applications folder to the Trash. Thank you for giving Sentient a try; it meant a lot to the two of us."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
