    "Open System Settings" : {
      "comment" : "A button that opens System Preferences → Login Items.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "OpenAI's official Codex command line tool. Sentient runs its cloud thinking through it, using your own ChatGPT subscription.\n\nInstall runs OpenAI's own installer; if codex is already there it simply updates in place, and your login and settings are untouched." : {
      "comment" : "Text describing the installation of the Codex CLI tool.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "OpenAI's official Codex command line tool. Sentient runs its cloud thinking through it, using your own ChatGPT subscription.\n\nInstall runs OpenAI's own installer; if codex is already there it simply updates in place, and your login and settings are untouched."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Официальный CLI Codex от OpenAI. Sentient запускает облачные рассуждения через него, используя вашу подписку ChatGPT.\n\nУстановка запускает собственный установщик OpenAI; если codex уже есть, он просто обновляется на месте — вход и настройки не трогаются."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "optional" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "optional"
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "по желанию"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Optional but recommended.\nLets Sentient see a screenshot of your screen the moment you fire a command, so it can see the thing you're asking about (“finish this”, “reply to this”).\n\nWithout it, you'll have to explicitly tell it which app you want it to start controlling." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Optional but recommended.\nLets Sentient see a screenshot of your screen the moment you fire a command, so it can see the thing you're asking about (“finish this”, “reply to this”).\n\nWithout it, you'll have to explicitly tell it which app you want it to start controlling."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "По желанию, но рекомендуется.\nПозволяет Sentient увидеть скриншот экрана в момент команды, чтобы понять, о чём речь («закончи это», «ответь на это»).\n\nБез этого нужно явно сказать, какое приложение контролировать."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Optional but recommended.\nLets Sidekick hear you and turn your words into text when you hold the shortcut key.\n\nWithout it, hold-to-talk stays off — you can still tap the key (or click the notch) and type.\n\nYour voice is heard and transcribed on this Mac, never in the cloud." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Optional but recommended.\nLets Sidekick hear you and turn your words into text when you hold the shortcut key.\n\nWithout it, hold-to-talk stays off — you can still tap the key (or click the notch) and type.\n\nYour voice is heard and transcribed on this Mac, never in the cloud."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "По желанию, но рекомендуется.\nПозволяет Sidekick слышать вас и превращать речь в текст при удержании горячей клавиши.\n\nБез этого hold-to-talk выключен — можно нажать клавишу (или кликнуть notch) и печатать.\n\nГолос слышится и расшифровывается на этом Mac, не в облаке."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Optional but recommended.\nLets Sidekick see a screenshot of your screen the moment you summon it, so it can see the thing you're asking about (“finish this”, “reply to this”).\n\nWithout it, you'll have to explicitly tell Sidekick which app you want it to start controlling." : {
      "comment" : "Tooltip for the screen recording checkbox.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Optional but recommended.\nLets Sidekick see a screenshot of your screen the moment you summon it, so it can see the thing you're asking about (“finish this”, “reply to this”).\n\nWithout it, you'll have to explicitly tell Sidekick which app you want it to start controlling."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Опционально, но рекомендуется.\nДаёт Sidekick снимок экрана в момент вызова, чтобы видеть то, о чём вы спрашиваете («сделай это», «ответь на это»).\n\nБез этого придётся явно сказать Sidekick, какое приложение начать контролировать."
          }
        }
      }
    },
