          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sentient never collects any of your personal data, nor any AI analysis of it. Privacy is a core principle that extends to every part of Sentient, and the whole stack will always remain open source." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
