    "Sentient runs on your own ChatGPT account through codex, and that login has stopped working. Log back in and I'll pick up right where we stopped." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sentient runs on your own ChatGPT account through codex, and that login has stopped working. Log back in and I'll pick up right where we stopped."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sentient работает через ваш аккаунт ChatGPT и Codex, и этот вход перестал работать. Войдите снова — продолжу с того же места."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sentient set up a small system helper so it could wake your Mac for the overnight run. macOS asks for your password to remove it; that is the same prompt you saw when it was installed. You can also skip it for now, and Sentient will still clear everything else." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sentient set up a small system helper so it could wake your Mac for the overnight run. macOS asks for your password to remove it; that is the same prompt you saw when it was installed. You can also skip it for now, and Sentient will still clear everything else."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sentient установил небольшой системный помощник, чтобы будить Mac для ночного запуска. macOS просит пароль, чтобы удалить его — тот же запрос, что при установке. Можно пропустить сейчас: Sentient всё равно очистит остальное."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sentient tried to send ChatGPT more than it accepts in one request. Your analysis is saved; if a retry hits this again, update Sentient OS and retry once more." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sentient tried to send ChatGPT more than it accepts in one request. Your analysis is saved; if a retry hits this again, update Sentient OS and retry once more."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sentient отправил ChatGPT больше, чем тот принимает за раз. Анализ сохранён; если повторится — обновите Sentient OS и попробуйте снова."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sentient will unlock the full experience and take your word for it.\n\nNote that the ChatGPT Go plan does not offer enough Codex use to unlock the full experience." : {
