    "The cloud copy is deleted immediately and your AIs lose access. Your knowledge base stays safe on this Mac, and turning sharing back on restores the same link." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The cloud copy is deleted immediately and your AIs lose access. Your knowledge base stays safe on this Mac, and turning sharing back on restores the same link."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Облачная копия удаляется сразу, ИИ теряют доступ. База знаний остаётся на Mac; включение шаринга снова восстановит ту же ссылку."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Codex add-on that can click, type, and act on your Mac when you fire an action.\n\nSet up downloads OpenAI's official Codex Desktop app package straight from OpenAI (about 535 MB), lifts out its computer-use plugin, and wires it into Codex CLI on this Mac. No desktop app installs; nothing is hosted by us." : {
      "comment" : "Tooltip for the computer use setup button.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The Codex add-on that can click, type, and act on your Mac when you fire an action.\n\nSet up downloads OpenAI's official Codex Desktop app package straight from OpenAI (about 535 MB), lifts out its computer-use plugin, and wires it into Codex CLI on this Mac. No desktop app installs; nothing is hosted by us."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Дополнение Codex, которое может кликать, печатать и действовать на вашем Mac при запуске действия.\n\nНастройка скачивает официальный пакет Codex Desktop прямо у OpenAI (около 535 МБ), извлекает плагин computer-use и подключает его к Codex CLI на этом Mac. Приложение на рабочий стол не ставится; мы ничего не хостим."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The INITIAL / ITERATIVE buttons run every selected source (folders + opted chats + Apple Notes + Gmail + Calendar) through the iterative core. Select only one to test it alone." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the functionality of the source picker.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "The language of morning cards is set in Settings → System → Response language — it is applied automatically and is not edited here." : {
