    },
    "To keep doing things for you safely, Sentient always runs the latest version. This one's quick; one tap and you're set." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To keep doing things for you safely, Sentient always runs the latest version. This one's quick; one tap and you're set."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Чтобы безопасно помогать вам, Sentient всегда на последней версии. Это быстро; один тап — и готово."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "To stay helpful, your Sentient runs its on-device intelligence every night at 3 AM, and that can only happen if Sentient is already running. It's heavily optimized and stays out of your RAM and CPU the rest of the time.\n\nWe recommend leaving this on to keep your Sentient alive." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To stay helpful, your Sentient runs its on-device intelligence every night at 3 AM, and that can only happen if Sentient is already running. It's heavily optimized and stays out of your RAM and CPU the rest of the time.\n\nWe recommend leaving this on to keep your Sentient alive."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Чтобы оставаться полезным, ваш Sentient каждую ночь в 3:00 запускает локальный интеллект — и это возможно только если Sentient уже работает. Он сильно оптимизирован и почти не нагружает RAM и CPU остальное время.\n\nМы рекомендуем оставить это включённым, чтобы Sentient оставался живым."
          }
        }
      }
    },
